title: Road to Avonlea. Season 1
description:
The first season of this enchanting canadian tv-series. Quality isn't perfect, but acceptable. Names of the episodes:
 1. The journey begins
 2. The story girl earns her name
 3. The quarantine at Alexander Abraham's
 4. Materializing of Duncan
 5. Old lady Lloyd
 6. Proof of the pudding
 7. Aunt Abigail's beau
 8. Malcolm and the baby
 9. Conversions
10. Felicity's challenge
11. The blue chest of Arabella King
12. The witch of Avonlea
13. Nothing endures but change
